Morrison Utility For Sale at $407 Million, Sunday Times Reports

-- B y   G r a n t   S m i t h
-- 
2011-08-14T09:21:23Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-08-14/morrison-utility-for-sale-at-407-million-sunday-times-reports.html
Morrison Utility Services Ltd., a
contractor for  utility companies , has been offered for sale at
250 million pounds ($407 million), the  Sunday Times  reported,
without saying where it got the information.  Private-equity firms  Cognetas LLP  and Bregal Capital each
own 40 percent of Morrison, with the remaining 20 percent held
by management, the newspaper said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Grant Smith in London at 
 gsmith52@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Stephen Voss on   sev@bloomberg.net  